arguments.prompt: A whimsical and creative image depicting a marmot and a chimpanzee, exchanging gift wrapped packages. It features the distinctive, plump body shape of a marmot. The environment combines the natural habitat of a marmot with elements of a breakfast table setting, a river of warm, melted butter, with oversized utensils or plates peeking out from the lush, pancake-like foliage in the background, a towering pepper mill standing in for a tree.  As the sun rises in this fantastical world, it casts a warm, buttery glow over the scene. The creatures, content in their butter river, lets out a yawn. Nearby, a flock of birds take flight
